snippet.title: Sega 32X Longplay [001] Knuckles Chaotix
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: ScHlAuChi

When you play it the first time its weird, but over time the game grows on you and it turns out pretty nice :)

Unfortunately YT decided to convert it wrong and add an audio delay. To get a lag free video, please go to www.longplays.org and download the MKV version.
Thank you for your cooperation :) -
